{"word":"προαλής","slug":"προαλής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προαλής</b></el> <el>(προ-ᾰλής, ές) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἄλλομαι</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>springing forward</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>overhanging, abrupt</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> = <a href='S:προπετής'><el>προπετής</el></a>:— <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <el>προαλέστερον</el> <i>more eagerly</i>, <b><a href='S:Strabo'>Strab.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}